Short - Class in Short
The Short class provides a Java interface to the M-functions from the files: C:\\Users\\Julius Gruber\\Dropbox\\Master\\matlab\\functions\\shortFunction.m The Short.dispose() method must be called on a Short instance when it is no longer needed to ensure that native resources allocated by this class are properly freed.

ShortRemote - Interface in Short
The ShortRemote class provides a Java RMI-compliant interface to the M-functions from the files: C:\\Users\\Julius Gruber\\Dropbox\\Master\\matlab\\functions\\shortFunction.m The dispose() method must be called on a ShortRemote instance when it is no longer needed to ensure that native resources allocated by this class are properly freed, and the server-side proxy is unexported.
